{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/vkaujALtN1SZGr4M54selGTImVY.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":11700000,"genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Drama"},{"id":35,"name":"Comedy"}],"homepage":"https://www.filmfactoryentertainment.com/films/bitter-christmas/","id":1088548,"imdb_id":"tt28088049","origin_country":["ES"],"original_language":"es","original_title":"Amarga Navidad","overview":"After her mother dies in December, advertising director Elsa immerses herself in work to cope. When a panic attack forces her to take a break, she decides to travel to Lanzarote with her friend Patricia. The story of these women run parallel to that of a screenwriter and film director, exploring how life and fiction are inseparably linked, sometimes painfully so.","popularity":5.9038,"poster_path":"/eSrtLQa7s2y04aVugd9bV2hRJ3A.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":49,"logo_path":"/tlzPjqJjba2WjBaNGN1SZuJmbYj.png","name":"El Deseo","origin_country":"ES"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"ES","name":"Spain"}],"release_date":"2026-03-20","revenue":4755643,"runtime":112,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Spanish","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"You’re confusing fiction with reality.","title":"Bitter Christmas","video":false,"vote_average":6.479,"vote_count":73,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","title":"Autofiction","type":""}]}}